                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was watching with the prosecutor - I saw the prisoner come into the premises alone - I heard the bottles chink; we went up, and took him - he fell down, and dropped the bottles.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I did it from distress.</p>
